column1: Members of the French National Assembly born out of France
Number of jurisdictions by driving side
Number of dead people by month since 2000
Number of films starring leonardo Di caprio.
column2:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ?uri) 
WHERE {
 ?uri rdf:type dbo:Film .
        ?uri dbo:starring res:Leonardo_DiCaprio . 
}

column1: All museums (including subclass of museum) in Barcelona with coordinates
column2:
SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?name ?coord ?lat ?lon
WHERE
{
 hint:Query hint:optimizer "None" .
 ?item wdt:P131* wd:Q1492 .
 ?item wdt:P31/wdt:P279* wd:Q33506 .
 ?item wdt:P625 ?coord .
 ?item p:P625 ?coordinate .
 ?coordinate psv:P625 ?coordinate_node .
 ?coordinate_node wikibase:geoLatitude ?lat .
 ?coordinate_node wikibase:geoLongitude ?lon .
 SERVICE wikibase:label {
 bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "ca" .
 ?item rdfs:label ?name
 }
}
ORDER BY ASC (?name)
